<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>1e pagina recept finder</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
<h1>Welkom bij begin</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
<section class="finder">
    <form>
        <h2> Wat wil je vandaag eten? </h2>
    
        <input type="text">
    </form>
    <button> Zoeken</button>
    <p> Uitgebreid zoeken</p>
</section>
<div class="line-with-text">
    <span class="text">Of</span>
</div>
<div class="pop-up">
  <button id="close"> X</button>
  <h2> Welkom bij de Recepten zoeker!</h2>
  <p>De app om je kookkunsten te delen, recepten te vinden met je eigen ingrediënten en punten te scoren!</p>
  <a href="#">Volgende</a>
</div>
<section class="filter-begin">
  <h2>Filter op bepaalde categorieën</h2>
  <div class="filter-container">
    <input type="checkbox" id="vis" name="filter" value="vis">
    <label for="vis">Vis</label>

    <input type="checkbox" id="vlees" name="filter" value="vlees">
    <label for="vlees">Vlees</label>

    <input type="checkbox" id="italiaans" name="filter" value="italiaans">
    <label for="italiaans">Italiaans</label>

    <input type="checkbox" id="glutenvrij" name="filter" value="glutenvrij">
    <label for="glutenvrij">Glutenvrij</label>

    <input type="checkbox" id="vegetarisch" name="filter" value="vegetarisch">
    <label for="vegetarisch">Vegetarisch</label>

    <input type="checkbox" id="halal" name="filter" value="halal">
    <label for="halal">Halal</label>

    <input type="checkbox" id="veganistisch" name="filter" value="veganistisch">
    <label for="veganistisch">Veganistisch</label>

</div>
  <button id="filter-submit">Toon recepten</button>
</section>
    </main>

    <script src="server.js"></script>


</body>

 <!-- css van de recept finder page -->
<style>
/*  gedeelte hier is de pop up  */
div .pop-up {
background-color: rgb(170, 191, 255);
font-family: sans-serif;
padding: 20px;
}

.pop-up h2 {
  font-size: 20px;
}

.pop-up {
    display: none; 
    background-color: white;
    width: 300px;
    height: 400px;
    padding: 30px 40px;
    position: absolute;
    transform: translate(-50%, 50%); 
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    border-radius: 1em;
    text-align: center;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease-out, opacity 0.5s ease-out;
}

.pop-up.show {
    display: block;
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}



.pop-up button {
  display: block;
  margin:0 0 20px auto;
  background: transparent;
  font-size: 30px;
  border-radius: 100%;
  width:40px;
height: 40px;
border: none;
outline: none;
cursor: pointer;
background-color: rgb(117, 117, 117);
color: white;
} 




.pop-up p {
 font-size: 14px;
 margin: 20px 0;
 line-height: 20px;
}

.pop-up a{
    position: relative; 
top: 10px;
    background-color: rgb(121, 121, 121);
    padding: 10px 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
    display: block;
    width: 150px;
    margin: 10px auto;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 2em;
}  
  /*  gedeelte hier is de pop up  */
  
  /* Gedeelte hier is algemeen van de pagina */
* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
  color: #333;
  line-height: 1.6;
  padding: 20px;
}

.finder {
  padding: 0 15px;
}

.finder input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 20px;
  margin: 10px 0 1em;
  border: none;
  background-color: #c8c8c8;
  color: white;
  border-radius: 1em;
}

button {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  background-color: #444;
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 10px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.line-with-text {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  margin: 4em 0;
}

.line-with-text::before,
.line-with-text::after {
  content: "";
  flex: 1;
  border-top: 1px solid #9d9d9d;
}

.text {
  padding: 0 10px;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #ff0000;
}


.filter-container input[type="checkbox"] {
  display: none;
}

.filter-container label {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background-color: #bebebe;
  color: white;
  border-radius: 10px;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin: 5px;
  text-align: center;
  transition: background-color 0.3s;
}

.filter-container label:hover,
.filter-container input[type="checkbox"]:checked + label {
  background-color: #ff0000;
}

.filter-begin ul {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  list-style: none;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

.filter-begin li {
  padding: 15px 20px;
  background-color: #bebebe;
  color: white;
